      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just not that simple though. \"reaching out\" to people who've already seen the stuff they've seen and judged me? i feel like the damage is already done. like no matter what i do, everyone already has an opinion of me and it's all bad. it feels like there's no version of the future where this actually gets better. it just feels like a loop of me being humiliated over and over. it's like i'm just trapped in this nightmare and there's no way out.",
